verbose_text: Moreover, the protein expression of the proteolytic enzymes MMP-9, MMP-13 and TIMP-1 was also increased in the lung tissues of hypoxic rats, indicating that hypoxia facilitates the accumulation of mast cells, and activates collagen metabolism and vascular remodeling in vivo (XREF_FIG).
